OL,3,CQueen's had Epstein victims 'in mind'
OL,4,Cin message to sexual abuse survivors
OL,6,FQueen Camilla has told survivors of
OL,7,Fsexual abuse that they are not alone,
OL,8,Fand had the victims of Jeffrey
OL,9,FEpstein's multiple crimes at the
OL,10,Fforefront of her mind during her
OL,11,Fspeech, it is understood.
OL,13,FCamilla had gathered influential
OL,14,Ffemale leaders at St James' Palace on
OL,15,FTuesday in her role as President of
OL,16,Fthe Women of the World organisation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
