OL,3,CQueen's had Epstein victims 'in mind'
OL,4,Cin message to sexual abuse survivors
OL,6,FMadame Pelicot and the Queen met at
OL,7,FClarence House last week.
OL,9,FCamilla said her guest had shared her
OL,10,Fstory with "grace, strength and, above
OL,11,Fall, determination that the world's
OL,12,Fview of violence against women and
OL,13,Fgirls must shift dramatically."
OL,15,FThe Queen also spoke directly to one
OL,16,Fof member of the audience, Amy Hunt,
OL,17,Fwhose mother and sisters were murdered
OL,18,Fin their own home.
OL,20,FThe ex-boyfriend of Amy's sister
OL,21,FLouise killed them in their own home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
