OL,3,CQueen's had Epstein victims 'in mind'
OL,4,Cin message to sexual abuse survivors
OL,6,FHe has consistently denied any
OL,7,Fwrongdoing.
OL,9,FHe was arrested and released by police
OL,10,Finvestigating misconduct in public
OL,11,Foffice last month.
OL,13,FIn closing her speech on Tuesday, the
OL,14,FQueen quoted Gisele Pelicot's words
OL,15,Fand said we all needed to bring about
OL,16,F"a collective awakening."
